3
00:02:01,311 --> 00:02:03,228
Hi, Frankie.

4
00:02:03,853 --> 00:02:05,103
Hello.

5
00:02:14,436 --> 00:02:15,728
Get in there.

6
00:02:37,436 --> 00:02:41,103
Nothing like that first
drink of the day.

7
00:02:42,228 --> 00:02:43,478
Go on, drink up. Enjoy.

8
00:02:43,853 --> 00:02:45,103
Hey, what's he doing, huh?

9
00:02:46,103 --> 00:02:47,519
Hey, they tell me you're
some dancer.

10
00:02:48,144 --> 00:02:49,728
Well, how about a little
dance anyway?

11
00:02:50,478 --> 00:02:51,228
