the big idea?!

15
00:03:22,269 --> 00:03:23,644
Frankie!

16
00:03:23,978 --> 00:03:24,561
Frankie!

17
00:03:24,853 --> 00:03:26,144
Frankie, when'd you get back?

18
00:03:26,478 --> 00:03:27,436
How are ya'?

19
00:03:28,186 --> 00:03:29,311
You all right?

20
00:03:29,519 --> 00:03:30,311
Y'know?

21
00:03:31,269 --> 00:03:32,311
The monkey's gone.

22
00:03:32,978 --> 00:03:33,978
Lemme look at ya.

23
00:03:34,228 --> 00:03:35,478
Lemme look at ya!

24
00:03:35,561 --> 00:03:38,603
Nah! Not even a posty-card!

25
00:03:39,353 --> 00:03:40,603
You can't read, anyway.

26
00:03:40,644 --> 00:03:43,061
Well, you could have drawed pictures?

27
00:03:43,103 --> 00:03:44,728
Ah, YOU goofy punk.

28
00:03:45,019 --> 00:03:46,186
