I tell ya, folks just don't have that trust
in their fellow man any more.

32
00:03:54,436 --> 00:03:55,103
Y'know what I mean?

33
00:03:56,728 --> 00:03:58,019
Hey, Antek?

34
00:03:58,478 --> 00:04:00,228
- Look who's out.
- Frankie!

35
00:04:01,394 --> 00:04:02,144
You all right?

36
00:04:02,603 --> 00:04:03,561
- Clean?
- Yep.

37
00:04:03,644 --> 00:04:04,228
Good kid.

38
00:04:04,269 --> 00:04:05,853
Enough, already. Buy me a drink.

39
00:04:05,894 --> 00:04:06,436
Sure.

40
00:04:06,686 --> 00:04:08,436
Hey, look what the cat
dragged in.

41
00:04:08,519 --> 00:04:09,936
Frankie, honey!

42
00:04:10,061 --> 00:04:12,769
You were gone so long I thought
